  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/7093a434ce676b42acc742f4ff3dd064.poster.avif?t=1772766720\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/7093a434ce676b42acc742f4ff3dd064.webm?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/7093a434ce676b42acc742f4ff3dd064.mp4?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the mysterious Canadian detective competition! Find clues, interview suspects, and find out the truth with your teammates' unique methods!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six Files  await you in the full game, containing convoluted puzzles from Canada’s most devious masterminds. Each one takes around 2-4 hours to complete depending on your skill of deduction…  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your time starts… now. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yours, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Game-master</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/39ef5faafbff14fca506a972ebadc5b4.avif?t=1772766720\" width=600 height=93 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve crimes with five unique methods</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/2c63523a4a2e410e336f482e1e56c910.poster.avif?t=1772766720\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/2c63523a4a2e410e336f482e1e56c910.webm?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/2c63523a4a2e410e336f482e1e56c910.mp4?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Refute faulty theories with evidence</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/88858343cade8c3131658edbf9fa78f1.poster.avif?t=1772766720\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/88858343cade8c3131658edbf9fa78f1.webm?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/88858343cade8c3131658edbf9fa78f1.mp4?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And More!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic Storytelling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich Character Depth</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distinctive Artwork</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Game World</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prequel to Methods: The Detective Competition<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/d56808f793c6942e8dc695bcc8282b3e.poster.avif?t=1772766720\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/d56808f793c6942e8dc695bcc8282b3e.webm?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/d56808f793c6942e8dc695bcc8282b3e.mp4?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing <strong>Methods: The Detective Competition</strong> first is highly recommended, but not required to understand the story.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/7093a434ce676b42acc742f4ff3dd064.poster.avif?t=1772766720\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/7093a434ce676b42acc742f4ff3dd064.webm?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/7093a434ce676b42acc742f4ff3dd064.mp4?t=1772766720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the mysterious Canadian detective competition! Find clues, interview suspects, and find out the truth with your teammates' unique methods!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six Files  await you in the full game, containing convoluted puzzles from Canada’s most devious masterminds. Each one takes around 2-4 hours to complete depending on your skill of deduction…  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your time starts… now. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yours, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Game-master</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/39ef5faafbff14fca506a972ebadc5b4.avif?t=1772766720\" width=600 height=93 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve crimes with five unique methods</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063530/extras/2c63523a4a2e410e336f482e1e56c910.poster.avif?t=1772766720\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse